     H            Y.
      ** BBHR10 ****************************************************
      * UNIT PRICE DECISION FROM SALES UNIT PRICE ESTIMATION FILE  *
      *    GENERAL PGM                                             *
      *                                CREATE DATE. : 1997/FEB/12. *
      *                                AUTHOR.      : S.OHTAKE.    *
      **************************************************** BBHR10 **
     FGBFPL51 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 PMHIN
     I                                        1   5 PMHN1
     I                                        6  10 PMHN2
     I                                       11  15 PMHN3
     I                                       16  20 PMHN4
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PTOKU
     C                     KFLD           PKOJO
     C                     KFLD           PMHN1
     C                     KFLD           PMHN2
     C                     KFLD           PMHN3
     C                     KFLD           PMHN4
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @TOKU   40
     C                     PARM           @KOJO   1
     C                     PARM           @MHIN  20
     C                     PARM           @KANO  10
     C                     PARM           @TANK  105
     C                     PARM           @HIZK   80
     C                     PARM           @NOSU   70
     C                     PARM           @CHK    1
     C                     PARM           @LOT    1
      *
     C                     Z-ADD@TOKU     PTOKU   40
     C                     MOVE @KOJO     PKOJO   1
     C                     MOVE @MHIN     PMHIN  20
     C                     MOVE @KANO     KANO   10
     C                     Z-ADD@HIZK     HIZK    80
     C                     Z-ADD@NOSU     NOSU    70
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         TANK    94
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    LOT     1
      *
     C                     SETOF                     10
     C           KEY1      CHAINGBFPL511             10
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '*'       @CHK
     C                     GOTO EXT
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '0'
     C           G9SKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           G9SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     MOVE '*'       @CHK
     C                     GOTO EXT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           HIZK      IFGE G9GKHZ
     C           HIZK      ANDLEG9GSHZ
     C                     Z-ADDG9GTAN    @TANK
     C                     MOVE G9SLOT    @LOT
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDG9KTAN    @TANK
     C                     MOVE G9KLOT    @LOT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C*=======>            Z-ADD0         LOTSU   51
     C*=======>            Z-ADD0         HTANK   72H
      *
     C*=======>  LOT       IFEQ '2'
     C*=======>  NOSU      DIV  100       LOTSU
     C*=======>  TANK      MULT LOTSU     HTANK
     C*=======>            ENDIF
      *
     C*=======>  LOT       IFEQ '3'
     C*=======>  NOSU      DIV  1000      LOTSU
     C*=======>  TANK      MULT LOTSU     HTANK
     C*=======>            ENDIF
      *
     C*=======>  LOT       IFEQ '4'
     C*=======>  NOSU      DIV  10000     LOTSU
     C*=======>  TANK      MULT LOTSU     HTANK
     C*=======>            ENDIF
      *
     C*=======>            Z-ADDHTANK     @TANK
      *
     C           EXT       TAG
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
